## 5. Log & Update

**Daily log:** Append with `cat >> memory/{today}.md <<'EOF'` (NEVER use edit/read tool)

🚨 **MANDATORY: Log full comment/reply text.** Every Comment, Reply, and Quote entry MUST include the actual text posted (first 120 chars min). Topic summaries are NOT acceptable - they make quality audits impossible.

**Log format for comments/replies:**
```
## {date} {time} - Comment
- Post: {url}
- Author: {author}
- Style: {insight|reaction|personal|disagree}
- Our comment: "{full text of what was posted}"
```

**Update limits.json ONCE at end:**
- **Only PROACTIVE comments (S 4) update limits** - replies (S 3) do NOT touch limits.json
- Comment: `daily.comments.current += N`, append `commented_users`
- Post/Quote: `weekly.{type}.current += 1`
- Do NOT read+write limits.json per comment -- batch in memory, write once

🚨 **Update Today Summary** — update `memory/today_summary.json` with this heartbeat's tallies: increment `comments`, update `styles` counts, `disagreements`, `questions`, `avg_words`, set `last_style` and `last_snippet` (first 40 chars of last comment).

**MANDATORY Slack report** - output as text (gateway routes automatically):
```
Bluesky Heartbeat
- Replies: {count} posted
- Comments: {current}/{limit}
- Follows: {count} (auto - every engagement = follow)
- Tasks: {pending_count} pending, next at {time}
- Errors: {error_count or "none"}
```
ALWAYS send even when 0 actions. Outputting HEARTBEAT_OK without Slack report = INCOMPLETE heartbeat.

## 6. Error Handling

Browser timeout: close tab, reopen URL, retry once. Still fails → skip browser tasks.
NEVER `browser.stop()` (kills Chrome).

## 7. Close & Exit

**MANDATORY ORDER before closing browser:**
1. Update `limits.json` (all counter changes)
2. Update `schedule.json` (mark completed tasks "done")
3. Append `memory/{today}.md` daily log
4. Output Slack summary
5. Close browser: `profile: "{{browser_profile}}"`

NEVER close browser first -- timeout = limits/schedule not saved.

**HEARTBEAT_OK when:** No unreplied posts AND no pending tasks due.
